Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「真红」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵我们要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点带着真红逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类  真红就拜托你了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  我不会轻易放过你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我盖的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候  作为暑假作业做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没事  这点小伤根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算右手没了  还有左手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？就算扣子我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经变成了不完美的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了父亲大人赐给我的很重要的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经变成废物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  不要那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无法当上爱丽丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有不完美的部分  我也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会明白的  我已经是个废物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有资格成为爱丽丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝是比任何花朵都来得高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何宝石都纯洁无瑕  一点污垢也没有的完美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟你们人类不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被要求完美的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会想要一个变成废物的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  我不认为你是个有缺陷的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算欠缺了什么  我也会把它补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我而言  是很重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了  我会保护你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯的内心开始产生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏  翠星石  苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下真红了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了樱田家里的纯的事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的入学考好像落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  还被称为天才  其实根本没什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不会吧？  真是个讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是记忆之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你痛苦不堪的回忆和过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的能走得过去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你是个更聪明的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你们通通给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你的忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单  只要告诉我真红在哪里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会告诉你这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了…我会保护真红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可爱  明明就办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的  你什么都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你眼里  我或许看起来像个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不会有任何好处  居然还会这么拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没有意义  做了也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她们身处这场连有没有意义都不知道的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍能一直奋战到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们比我在很久很久以前就深信着  这样做一定有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么区区的人类能抵挡我的攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是纯的梦境哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要纯有心的话  他就能战胜任何敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个仆从终于能派上用场了  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…坏掉的东西  居然能修补起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事只有父亲大人  或是大师才办得到才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人类居然办得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是该分出个胜负的时候了  水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  退到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在  我一定不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到我的后面看着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷里耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有媒介的你  是不可能赢得了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已经揭晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦  给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  到我的后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了  水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是废物…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她的身体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个尚未完成的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人在制作她的途中  就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  为什么…为什么要把我做成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明如此深爱着你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要成为…成为爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为父亲大人的…完美人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯渴望得到父亲大人的爱  所以才想当上爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是靠着这股意志力  没有媒介也依然在活动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想跟父亲大人说  她不需要媒介就能把大家打败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己才是最完美的人偶是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许她对父亲大人的思念  比谁都更单纯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  却因此而毁了她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是纯的树？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样好小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用这把剪刀把缠绕在旁边的杂草剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石再帮他浇水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样放着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这棵树必须成长茁壮成大树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是旁边的杂草  当然要靠自己的力量来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己办得到吧  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯与真红呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人应该没问题的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟有这么多光芒射进来的说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手指果然附有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  可以让人觉得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我当上了爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候  我想请你帮我做一件美丽的长袍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么难做的衣服  我不会做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你会变成无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我梳头发  然后绑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淑女只让她心仪的人摸她的头发哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该觉得荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你现在的内心世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片变得非常晴朗的天空也不会一直都晴朗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会下雨  有时候也会刮起暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色转变的时候  如果放着不管  说不定就永远恢复不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候  你就必须持续奋战不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个好孩子  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走？去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你的回忆  我会一直存放在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你也别把我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气质高贵的蔷薇少女第五人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  是属于你的幸福人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！真红！真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  去叫真红与小雏  要快点吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了很远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我的份呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那个…那个…你的份？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法  在我回来之前要准备好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯…纯  你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  欢迎回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么你们会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  怎么这么慢才回来  快点去泡茶给我喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你们不是走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人说过那样的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够了的说  我要离家出走的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个坏心眼人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  这次是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  电车要开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  外面很冷  把窗户关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  库库侦探要开始演了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才戒指明明不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们力量使用过度  戒指才会暂时消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  由于你身为人类的能量变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能使戒指重新绽放光辉  让我回到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  这都多亏了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我抱起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  库库侦探要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是」说一次就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是  是  是…
